author: National Geographic
description: Looking to cut back on your drinking? Alzo Slade examines what effect a dry month has on your body in What Does Alcohol Do To My Body?—the first episode of National Geographic's all-new YouTube Original Series, #WhatDoesXDoToMyBody. Now available on the Nat Geo YouTube Channel.
title: Could a dry month help you quit drinking? #WhatDoesXDoToMyBody
